Package HMS.src.appointment

Class AppointmentOutcome

java.lang.Object
HMS.src.appointment.AppointmentOutcome
public class AppointmentOutcome extends Object
Represents the outcome of an appointment, including details such as service type, diagnosis, and prescriptions.

      public AppointmentOutcome(String appointmentID, LocalDate appointmentDate, String serviceType, String diagnosis, ArrayList<Prescription> prescriptions, String consultationNotes, Doctor doctor)
      Constructor for creating a new appointment outcome.
      Parameters:
      appointmentID - Unique identifier for the appointment.
      appointmentDate - Date of the appointment.
      serviceType - Type of service provided (e.g., Consultation, Surgery).
      diagnosis - Diagnosis determined during the appointment.
      prescriptions - List of prescriptions issued during the appointment.
      consultationNotes - Notes from the consultation.
      doctor - Doctor responsible for the appointment.
